The paper focuses on visual tasks such as scene recognition and domain adaptation, which are typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) field. The paper also discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (CNN) and dictionary-based models, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image and video processing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it discusses feature extraction and representation.
